title: No New MIssions
body: I completed the first mission ("In the beginning..."), and no new missions have come up since the missions thing was even first published on live servers. Can someone please give me a fix? I cant figure out why Im unable to see other missions even though I completed the first one.

replies.body: Missions have stopped for the time being since the [**Vs Event has ended**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/2BvE9WwM-vs-event-conclusion). Be on the lookout for missions to return sometime in the future!
